    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Levana 是一款心理恐怖游戏，你将从月球宇航员的视角体验</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141360/extras/f797f5a087c607536cd8bdf5858ae7cf.poster.avif?t=1764201783\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141360/extras/f797f5a087c607536cd8bdf5858ae7cf.webm?t=1764201783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141360/extras/f797f5a087c607536cd8bdf5858ae7cf.mp4?t=1764201783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Levana</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>Levana</strong> 中，你在飞船内，需要根据无线电指示执行各种任务。你可以使用不同的物品来完成这些任务，并且要小心，因为有些事情是你<strong>没有被告知的</strong>。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩法</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levana 是一款具有不同任务机制的第一人称写实模拟游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特点</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >气氛环境和写实图形</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >复古 VHS 美学</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏仅支持16:9比例分辨率（不支持超宽屏）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
